  "prompt": "Where can I learn Spanish in Delhi?",
  "response": "There are several places in Delhi where you can learn Spanish, ranging from language institutes to universities. Here are some options:\n\n1. **Instituto Cervantes**: This is the official Spanish government cultural institution that offers Spanish language courses for all levels.\n\n2. **Delhi University**: Some colleges under Delhi University offer Spanish language courses as part of their curriculum.\n\n3. **Language Schools**:\n   - **Language Academy**: Offers Spanish courses for beginners to advanced levels.\n   - **Inlingua**: Known for its language training, Inlingua offers Spanish language programs.\n   - **Berlitz**: Offers personalized language training, including Spanish.\n\n4. **Online Platforms**: Websites like **Duolingo**, **Rosetta Stone**, and **Babbel** provide language learning opportunities that can supplement in-person classes.\n\n5. **Private Tutors**: You might also consider hiring a private tutor for personalized lessons. Websites like **UrbanPro** can help you find tutors in your area.\n\nMake sure to check for reviews and the curriculum offered by each institution to choose the one that best fits your learning style and schedule.",
